data.description: Discover the perfect blend of space and comfort.  Nestled in the heart of Pinellas Park, this property has been lovingly updated and well-maintained. Catering to large gatherings, the home offers a spacious kitchen, two living areas, and a dining space conveniently located near the kitchen. The bathrooms shine with updated vanities, and each bedroom is a spacious sanctuary. Step outside to the massive fenced backyard, where there's abundant space for a future pool, making it your private haven for relaxation or vibrant cookouts. Additional features include a single-car garage and energy-efficient solar panels.
